column1: Gus_263,"2008-03-25T15:32:21.623Z","Knights of  the classic castle sets","This set is a pack with four minifigures, so, this is a little castle set, released in the year of 1983. One of the first in the castle sets, the castle figures are simple but also nicely designed. All have the yellow lego characteristic face. Two have a red, gray and blue color on the &quot
column3: (body and legs) and the two other have a black and red &quot
column5: . The helmets are good designed and stay very well in the minifigure. Two helmets are used also on most recently castle sets and other two are from old times, but they still great with their desogn, that looks like a paladin's helmet. This set also includes for increase the knights, one shield, sword, a little axe and a medium sized axe. Altough the set includes only four minifigures and some itens and the playability is the same of a figure pack, all the pieces are useful, awesome and this set can increase so much other classic castle sets with the weapons and minifigures. So, i rate the Castle Figures 5/5",FALSE,5,0,0,0,0
